- `Invincible/backend/src/app/core/track_vectorizer.py` — NEW, ~250 LOC. Per-target deque(maxlen=8) of recent fixes; `heading_for(tkey)` derives bearing from last 2 fixes >=5 m apart; `implied_speed_mps`; `arrow_feature(tkey)` builds LineString geometry with arrowhead vertices, length scaled by confidence (20 m floor -> 80 m at conf=1.0); `bulk_arrow_collection(min_confidence, max_age_ms)` returns a GeoJSON FeatureCollection with layer=`leo_red_arrow`, symbol=`RED_ARROW`.
- `Invincible/backend/src/app/core/waze_verification.py` — NEW, ~230 LOC. Explainable verification scorer: `raw_signal = SUM time_weight * spatial_weight * upvote_uplift`, then `score = 1 - exp(-raw/tau)` with `tau=1.6` so ~4 strong recent Waze pins saturate to >=0.95. 90-min half-life on time weight, linear roll-off on spatial weight, 30-s in-memory report cache. `score_track()` returns `VerificationResult` with full evidence list; `verification_report(candidates)` ranks descending by score.
- `Invincible/backend/src/app/db/database.py` — added `arion_approach_alerts` + `arion_approach_active` table DDL into central `init_db()` (so tables exist on first boot, not just lazily on first ledger call). Three indexes added.
- `Invincible/backend/src/app/api/arion.py` — added imports for the three new core modules + `asyncio`/`json`. Added `_collect_classified_candidates(window_hours)` helper that builds a unified candidate list from MAID precinct-residents + FirstNet leaked-heartbeat IPs + SSID-probe LEA devices AND side-effect-feeds the vectorizer so heading data accumulates. **12 NEW endpoints** (all under existing `/arion` mount, additive to the 109 pre-existing routes — total now 121):
  - `GET  /arion/approach-alerts/active` — currently-fired un-acked alerts
  - `GET  /arion/approach-alerts/history` — ledger replay with limit/since_ms/band filters
  - `POST /arion/approach-alerts/{alert_id}/ack` — operator acknowledgment
  - `POST /arion/approach-alerts/clear` — manual clear by target_key
  - `POST /arion/approach-alerts/evaluate` — drive one eval pass (15-s HUD cadence)
  - `GET  /arion/approach-alerts/audio-manifest` — deterministic cue->wav/tts mapping
  - `GET  /arion/approach-alerts/stats` — ledger stats
  - `GET  /arion/approach-alerts/stream` — SSE push stream (configurable interval_s)
  - `GET  /arion/leo-precision/red-arrows` — directional-arrow GeoJSON FeatureCollection (confidence-scaled shaft length)
  - `GET  /arion/leo-precision/red-arrows/stats` — vectorizer stats
  - `GET  /arion/leo-precision/verification` — per-track Waze verification scores + evidence list
  - `GET  /arion/leo-precision/verification/stats` — scorer stats

