         row carries the encounter peak plus the operator nearest route
         point (within +/- 60s) so the WinUI HUD can paint both layers in
         one fetch.
  GET    /replay/target/{target_key}/pattern-of-life
         24-hour UTC histogram + 7-day weekday histogram + dwell stats
         (median/p90/min/max), RSSI median/p90, confidence median, and top
         10 quantized (50m cell) location buckets. Empty-target degrades
         to {encounter_count: 0, top_locations: []}.
  GET    /replay/target/{target_key}/co-occurrence?min_overlap_ms=1000
         Other targets whose [start,end] intervals overlap the anchor by
         at least min_overlap_ms. Returns overlap_ms, co_encounters,
         share_of_anchor for each. Sorted by overlap_ms desc.
  GET    /replay/target/{target_key}/anomalies?sigma_hour=2.0&sigma_dist_m=500
         Encounters flagged unusual_hour (hour-bucket below 1/(24*sigma)
         of fleet mass) and/or unusual_place (distance from median(lat,lon)
         > sigma_dist_m). Returns flags + dist_from_median_m + baseline
         envelope. No raise on sparse data.
  GET    /replay/target/{target_key}/cross-session
         Per-session appearance count + first/last_seen + rssi_max for this
         target. Sessions sorted most-recent first; includes session_label
         in the Replay-page format.
  GET    /replay/target/{target_key}/dwell
         Per-encounter dwell-time analysis: total_dwell_ms + median/p90/p99/
         max + full encounter breakdown.
  GET    /replay/time-cursor?ts_ms=X&window_ms=30000
         Snapshot of every encounter active at ts_ms +/- window_ms, plus
         operator nearest route point and the session boundary the cursor
         falls into. window_ms capped at 10 minutes.
  GET    /replay/session-summary?start_ms=X&end_ms=Y
         Rollup for a time window: encounter_count, unique_targets, route_
         point_count, top_targets/labels/device_types, bbox, centroid.
  GET    /replay/density-grid?start_ms=X&end_ms=Y&cell_m=100
