         (10m to 10km). Each cell carries count, unique_targets, rssi_max,
         and quantized lat/lon. Cells sorted by count desc; limit cap.
  POST   /replay/bookmarks
         Operator annotation at a specific ts_ms. Body: BookmarkIn(ts_ms,
