         endpoint resolves the enclosing session and the nearest route
         point (+/- 60s) and stamps lat/lon onto the bookmark row.
  GET    /replay/bookmarks?start_ms&end_ms&target_key
         List/filter bookmarks. Default ORDER BY ts_ms ASC, limit 500
         (max 5000).
  DELETE /replay/bookmarks/{bookmark_id}
         Remove a bookmark. Returns {deleted: rowcount}.
  GET    /replay/health
         status / encounter_total / route_point_total / bookmark_total /
         session_count / capabilities[].

Sidecar table (additive, IF NOT EXISTS, lazy bootstrap at first call):
  replay_bookmarks
    (id PK, ts_ms, label, color?, note?, target_key?, session_start_ms?,
     session_end_ms?, lat?, lon?, created_ms, author?)
  Indexes: idx_rbm_ts(ts_ms), idx_rbm_tkey(target_key).

